<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قصيدة في غربة الإسلام:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَقُولُ وَأَوْلَى مَا يُرَى فِي الدَّفَاتُرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَأَحْسَنُ فَيْضاً مِنْ عُيُونِ الْمَحَابِرِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>هُوَ الْحَمْدُ لِلْمَعْبُودِ وَالشُّكْرُ وَالثَّنَاء<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَقَدَّسَ عَنْ قَوْلِ الْغُوَاةِ الْغَوَادِرِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَجَلَّ عَنْ الأَنْدَادِ لا رَبَّ غَيْرُهُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَعَنْ شَافِعٍ فِي الابْتِدَا أَوْ مُوَازِرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَصَلَّى عَلَى مَنْ قَامَ للهِ دَاعِياً<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَشَيَّدَ أَعْلامَ الْهُدَى وَالشَّعَائِرِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَوْضَحَ دِينَ اللهِ مِنْ بَعْدِ مَا سَفَتْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>عَلَيْهِ السَّوَافِي فِي الْقُرَى وَالْجَزَائِرِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَعَادَا وَوَالَى فِي رِضَى اللهِ قَوْمَهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَلَمْ يَثْنِه عَنْ ذَاكَ صَوْلَةُ قَاهِرِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مُحَمَّدٌ الْمُبْعُوثُ لِلنَّاسِ رَحْمةً<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>نِذَارَتُهُ مَقْرونَةٌ بِالْبَشَائِرِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَبَعْدُ فَإِنْ تَعْجَب لِخَطْبٍ تَبَلْبَلَتْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِفَادِحِهِ أَهْلُ النُّهَى وَالْبَصَائِرِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَلا عَجَبًا يَوْمٌ مِنَ الدَّهْرِ مِثْلَ مَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَنَاخَ بِنَا مِنْ كُلِّ بَادٍ وَحَاضِرِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَمَا ذَاكَ إِلا غُرْبَةُ الدِّينِ يَا لَهَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مُصِيبَةُ قَوْمٍ مِنْ عِظَامِ الْفَوَاقِرِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>